description:
For an international project in Chennai, we are urgently looking for an Azure Integration Services Ddeveloper responsible for implementing various enterprise integration components with working experience in Cloud Technologies (preferably Azure) in Data engineering and Machine learning.










 We are looking for a motivated contractor. Candidates need to be fluent in English.










**Tasks and responsibilities:** 



* Design, build, and maintain secure, scalable, and observable integration solutions on Microsoft Azure using C\\# .NET and Azure Integration Services. The role will deliver business\\-critical integrations between internal systems, SaaS platforms, and partner endpoints, ensuring reliable messaging, robust APIs, and secure authentication via Microsoft Entra ID;
* Strong hands\\-on experience in Java;
* Experience on any of the search engines;
* Document Low Level Design, Unit Testing Plan, and Unit Test case documentation;
* Design, develop, code review, bug\\-fix, and test the application;
* Assist in Integration Testing;
* Perform Code optimization and strictly adhere to bank coding standards;
* Assist in any documentation or any artifacts needed for OIS clearance;
* Participate in SCRUM meeting work closely with onsite and offshore team;
* Perform timely resolution of issues and root cause analysis of each issue;
* Applied Security Compliance, which includes Application and data security assessment and remediation to attain compliance with WB Office Information Security Policies and Standards;
* Proactively manage your own work queue, time, and expectations, meet deadlines, and communicate needs and tradeoffs if your schedule is in jeopardy;









**Profile:** 



* Bachelor or Master degree;
* \\+6 years hands\\-on experience with C\\# .NET \\& Azure Integration Services (Logic Apps, Functions, Service Bus, Entra ID);
* Expert\\-level in Azure Logic Apps, Azure Functions, Azure Service Bus, Azure Storage Services, Web Services, REST;
* SQL understanding;
* Linux \\& Bash scripting experience is a plus;
* Must have experience in configuration management, release management, versioning and build process;
* Good analytical skills, Critical thinking, and Solid problem\\-solving abilities;
* Experience in application performance monitoring and optimizing;
* Fluent in English;
